20 in the possession of a person as authorized under the Nebraska Hemp
21 Farming Act, they are not considered hashish or concentrated cannabis for
22 purposes of the Uniform Controlled Substances Act.
23 (c) Hashish or concentrated cannabis does not include cannabidiol
